One of the most powerful signals that I look for on a daily basis is an "R2G" (a stock that opens red and flips to green). This simple signal gets amplified ten folds when the stock gaps down(opens red) on bad news(downgrade, earnings etc) and then flips to GREEN!  STRONG SIGNAL!

I love downgrades(sometimes called "Clowngrade").... because if the stock "ignores" the downgrade, 1 or 2 days later and attacks highs again, you know the breakout will be legit!   Especially if the downgrade is ignored on that very same day(not the case for $RIDE this time).

One of the most powerful signals that I look for on a daily basis is an "R2G" (a stock that opens red and flips to green). This simple signal gets amplified ten folds when the stock gaps down(opens red) on bad news(downgrade, earnings etc) and then flips to GREEN!  STRONG SIGNAL!

I love downgrades(sometimes called "Clowngrade").... because if the stock "ignores" the downgrade, 1 or 2 days later and attacks highs again, you know the breakout will be legit!   Especially if the downgrade is ignored on that very same day(not the case for $RIDE this time).
